				  </p>
            </entry>
          </row>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry colname="col1">
              <p>Step 1 
				  </p>
            </entry>
            <entry colname="col2">
              <p>Receive the Video Implementation Worksheet from the web
					 analytics team. 
				  </p>
            </entry>
            <entry colname="col3">
              <p>
                <xref href="video_worksheet.xml#concept_0A7B2FAC52B04AE6BFD8747B57D56222" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local" otherprops="onpage">
                  <?xm-replace_text Video Implementation Worksheet?>
                </xref>
              </p>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry colname="col1">
              <p>Step 2 
				  </p>
            </entry>
            <entry colname="col2">
              <p>Complete the tasks outlined in the section for your player.
					 The general process to measure video is as follows: 
				  </p>
              <ul id="ul_A6C568F7D7654EA082F4580DBA876367">
                <li id="li_13DC52C904F248E78D7DE7A5FD796C48">Download and link
						the AppMeasurement library that contains the media module. 
					 </li>
                <li id="li_289260E566F64675B760A5DF3A319D1A">Map the
						variables selected by your web analytics team. 
					 </li>
                <li id="li_1D7F2E6D67104608AADC5FE6ED7E84C8">Configure
						milestones. 
					 </li>
                <li id="li_B79D7716532545DB9F1801E715BD6C96">Track the events
						that occur in your player. 
					 </li>
              </ul>
              <p>Follow the link in the Details column for specific
					 instructions for your player. 
				  </p>
            </entry>
            <entry colname="col3">
              <ul id="ul_F47B64A2139E4F12856A6A45CADC58D3">
                <li id="li_D9AD7421CCA44AD0A133ABFF0B989FFF">
                  <xref href="video_flash.xml#task_2AF250F1F78444A99770F04353F96467" type="task" format="dita" scope="local" otherprops="onpage">
                    <?xm-replace_text Flash Video Playback?>
                  </xref>
                </li>
                <li id="li_8E0DBF6A9DC34EC6AB40507A84EE16E2">
